author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Propertylink Group HY ‍Profit After Tax Attributable $72.6 Mln, Up 145.1 Pct​

organizations.name: brief-propertylink group hy ‍profit after tax attributable

text:
Feb 13 (Reuters) - Propertylink Group:
* HY ‍PROFIT AFTER TAX ATTRIBUTABLE $72.6 MILLION, UP 145.1 PERCENT​
* ‍INTERIM DISTRIBUTION OF 3.6 CENTS PER STAPLED SECURITY​ * HY TOTAL REVENUE AND OTHER INCOME $101.5 MILLION, UP 48.8 PERCENT
* ‍DISTRIBUTABLE EARNINGS PER SECURITY FOR FY18 WILL BE 9.0 CENTS​
* DISTRIBUTION PER SECURITY FOR FY18 WILL TOTAL 7.3 CENTS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
